00:35:49.280 --> 00:35:51.510
was that she's down
to earth, and very,

00:35:51.510 --> 00:35:56.840
very straightforward and
focused, and no nonsense,

00:35:56.840 --> 00:35:59.099
and that's not always the
case in the filmy line.

00:35:59.099 --> 00:35:59.890
I'll tell you that.

00:35:59.890 --> 00:36:01.340
I think you can answer that.

00:36:01.340 --> 00:36:04.970
And so we are kind of the
un-filmy people, in that we're

00:36:04.970 --> 00:36:06.870
