out and doing crazy stuff.

00:36:10.314 --> 00:36:11.730
I mean, that's fun
once in awhile.

00:36:11.730 --> 00:36:15.090
But the bottom line is that
it has to be a balance.

00:36:15.090 --> 00:36:18.430
And so the answer
is, she was real.

00:36:18.430 --> 00:36:20.320
That's what mattered to me.

00:36:20.320 --> 00:36:23.540
And certainly with my career and
her career, the other comment

00:36:23.540 --> 00:36:27.450
