been everywhere and yet been

00:36:30.230 --> 00:36:31.080
nowhere.

00:36:31.080 --> 00:36:33.790
And what I mean by that is,
they closed the Eiffel Tower

00:36:33.790 --> 00:36:35.690
for one of her shoots.

00:36:35.690 --> 00:36:38.540
And, imagine that, the Eiffel
Tower-- the [INAUDIBLE],

00:36:38.540 --> 00:36:39.710
everything else.

00:36:39.710 --> 00:36:43.390
They went to a
glacier in Alaska,

00:36:43.390 --> 00:36:46.610
had multiple chopper setups,
and shooting for a movie

00:36:46.610 --> 00:36:49.850
called "Pukar," and
yet, for these guys,

00:36:49.850 --> 00:36:52.860
it's a matter of jetting in,
getting in hair and makeup,

00:36:52.860 --> 00:36:55.100
putting on your clothes,
and jetting out.

00:36:55.100 --> 00:36:58.820
So in the time we've been
married, the one kind of gift

00:36:58.820 --> 00:37:01.910
was that we could go
and do things normally.

