Which that doesn't
sound like a lot.

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:12.540
It sounds like a
chore to most people,

00:37:12.540 --> 00:37:15.685
but for someone like
this, it's like freedom.

00:37:15.685 --> 00:37:16.310
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:37:16.310 --> 00:37:17.530
I can imagine.

00:37:17.530 --> 00:37:18.559
AMIT SINGHAL: Thank you.

