you reflecting at some point--

00:37:34.290 --> 00:37:35.180
that you had make it?

00:37:35.180 --> 00:37:37.450
Cause there are a lot of men and
women in India and everywhere

00:37:37.450 --> 00:37:39.241
in the world, who want
to be where you are.

00:37:39.241 --> 00:37:42.940
And when did you feel,
yes, I've done it?

00:37:42.940 --> 00:37:46.150
MADHURI DIXIT-NENE:
My film called

00:37:46.150 --> 00:37:47.890
"Tezaab" was released
in '89, and I

00:37:47.890 --> 00:37:51.660
