and suddenly one of them says,

00:38:31.090 --> 00:38:33.750
Are you the [NON-ENGLISH] girl?

00:38:33.750 --> 00:38:34.460
I said, Yeah.

00:38:34.460 --> 00:38:36.260
Can we have an autograph?

00:38:36.260 --> 00:38:38.800
And I was so thrilled--
signing an autograph

00:38:38.800 --> 00:38:40.440
and somebody's recognized me.

00:38:40.440 --> 00:38:42.960
And I signed my name, and
I wrote Madhuri Dixit,

00:38:42.960 --> 00:38:44.010
and I gave it to him.

00:38:44.010 --> 00:38:46.260
And he turns to the other
guy and says, [NON-ENGLISH].

00:38:52.680 --> 00:38:54.850
So, yeah, that was the
first time I thought,

00:38:54.850 --> 00:38:57.492
oh my goodness, I made it.

00:38:57.492 --> 00:38:58.200
AMIT SINGHAL: OK.

